...the building blocks of creation
and says:

88
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,790
"Hello, maker of the universe.

89
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,438
I see what you did there.

90
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,158
Good one."

91
00:05:06,359 --> 00:05:07,553
Right.

92
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:10,917
Now, how would you characterize
your relationship with Mr. Wolowitz?

93
