Confidence, not exuding.

100
00:05:29,479 --> 00:05:32,039
Do you know of any groups
Mr. Wolowitz is a member of?

101
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:34,588
You are beautiful, you know that?

102
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:39,078
You pop, sparkle and buzz electric.

103
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,236
I'm gonna pick you up at 8.

104
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:46,471
Show you a night
you will never forget.

105
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,348
Sounds great.

106
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,512
Really?

107
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,234
Yeah.

108
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:55,790
Can my 6'2" Navy SEAL husband
come with us?

109
00:05:57,200 --> 00:06:01,637
Is that--? Oh, my, I didn't see the ring
with my glasses off, so....

110
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,273
Look at that, I'm starting to exude.

111
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,953
[CHUCKLES]

112
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,389
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

113
00:06:07,559 --> 00:06:10,790
LEONARD: Wanna get that?
-Not particularly.

114
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:15,038
-Could you get that?
-I suppose I could if I were asked.

115
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:16,189
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

116
00:06:16,359 --> 00:06:19,988
-Would you please get that?
-Well, of course.

117
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:24,436
